data.description: One of the most desirable streets in all of Brielle.  Homes in this area rarely become available!  Situated on tree-lined, private road, around the corner from exclusive Manasquan River Golf Club.  Custom built home boasts gorgeous 5 bedrooms and 4.5 luxurious baths, including a first floor bedroom/bath.  Stunning kitchen w/ custom-designed cherry wood cabinetry, stainless steel Viking appliances, glistening granite counters, dramatic great room, wetbar, and open floor plan for amazing entertaining.  Private backyard for summer enjoyment and plenty of room for a pool.  Mins. to beaches, restaurants, shopping, tennis, marinas, sailing, yacht club and golf.
